\end_inset

.
 Some of these are 
\begin_inset Formula \[
\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}\frac{1}{n\left(e^{2\pi nx}-1\right)}=\frac{1}{2}\sum_{m=1}^{\infty}\frac{\coth(\pi mx)-1}{m}\]

\end_inset

 
