\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}\frac{(-1)^{n}}{n\left(e^{2\pi nx}-1\right)}=\frac{1}{2}\sum_{m=1}^{\infty}(-1)^{m}\,\frac{\coth(\pi mx)-1}{m}\]

\end_inset

 
