\begin_inset Formula $P_{s}$
\end_inset

 can be re-written in terms of the Eisenstein series 
\begin_inset Formula $G_{1-s}$
\end_inset

, and the behaviour of one under the action of the modular group can be
 igven in terms of the other.
 
